00:19:06,540 --> 00:19:09,140
All we do, is feed that greed.

245
00:19:10,380 --> 00:19:13,620
And the greedier he is,
the more we can take him for.

246
00:19:15,100 --> 00:19:19,419
All we need to do now is plan
things and cover all the angles

247
00:19:19,420 --> 00:19:21,100
so there are no surprises.

248
00:19:28,180 --> 00:19:31,418
- So how we doing?
