"Fit" doesn't help, Sean.
Any clue what she does?

260
00:20:00,980 --> 00:20:02,939
No, no, it's OK, send 'em up.

261
00:20:02,940 --> 00:20:06,179
If you'd just like to take the
elevator up to the sixth floor,

262
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:08,760
