Thank you.

263
00:20:19,620 --> 00:20:23,020
Mr Wasem?
Perfect, right this way, please.

264
00:20:27,380 --> 00:20:29,019
Don't worry.
Don't worry, ok?

265
00:20:29,020 --> 00:20:32,179
Take this one. When you get
back, all right, just call me,

266
00:20:32,180 --> 00:20:35,820
- we'll talk about it. Ok?
- Ok. Ok. - Good, good.

267
00:20:48,860 --> 00:20:52,779
Mr Wasem.
Very pleased to meet you.

268
00:20:52,780 --> 00:20:56,380
This is my broker whilst I'm
in London, Yvonne Hammond.

269
00:20:57,340 --> 00:21:00,260
Ms Hammond.
A pleasure.

270
00:21:02,580 --> 00:21:07,299
So. Well, look, we can, er...
Oh, Henry, for God's sake, leave it.

271
00:21:07,300 --> 00:21:09,299
- Get out! - I'm sorry
- Get out! Out! Come on!

272
00:21:09,300 --> 00:21:11,339
How quickly can
you leave an office?

273
00:21:11,340 --> 00:21:15,299
Terribly sorry about that,
must be hire a cretin week.

274
00:21:15,300 --> 00:21:16,860
You stay.

275
00:21:21,540 --> 00:21:25,299
- I've been hearing a lot of good
things about you, Mr Cole. - Oh?

276
00:21:25,300 --> 00:21:28,539
People are very impressed with
the returns you've achieved

277
00:21:28,540 --> 00:21:30,259
and in such a short space of time.

278
00:21:30,260 --> 00:21:33,739
Well, that's the beauty
of the markets isn't it?

279
00:21:33,740 --> 00:21:37,099
I mean, if you're well informed
and you're, you're quick enough,

280
00:21:37,100 --> 00:21:38,460
all things are possible.

281
00:21:41,820 --> 00:21:44,220
They talk to you like you're
the lowest form of life.

282
00:21:44,221 --> 00:21:46,580
Want to know where you are
every minute of the day,

283
00:21:46,581 --> 00:21:50,259
run here, go there, do this, move that,
then they treat you like a muppet.

284
00:21:50,260 --> 00:21:52,979
I know everything he does.
I know how he makes his money

285
00:21:52,980 --> 00:21:55,299
and why everyone thinks
he's golden bollocks.

286
00:21:55,300 --> 00:21:57,619
What do I get for it?
